reviews.text: 這間是我在香港吃過最好吃的火鍋，湯底實在利害，放任何食材下去，口味都非常好，牛肉肉質不錯，丸子、響鈴等都相當好吃。

We had 麻婆&清湯？soup. We felt it was not too hot. But it’s coming later. lol. The ingredients are very fresh. We had 12 cans of beer as well.
It’s cost around $500/ppl. Good price & tasty.
